{"tid":410150,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢係咪愛我","createTime":"2017-09-22T16:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T16:04:45.000Z","uid":149162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfbcf923fe7bd5d35aa3dd5fb8aec691cc86c5a","tid":410150,"uid":149162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:01:23.000Z","msg":"男朋友同前度分咗手成年 <br />\n同我一齊時仲有聯絡 <br />\n佢之後應承我會斷<br />\n因為前度有抑鬱而唔斷住<br />\n後尾呃我話同男仔去旅行<br />\n第一次偷睇佢手機先知喺同前度去<br />\n未知嗰陣借錢俾佢去<br />\n到我踢爆佢<br />\n佢話喺為左我<br />\n想同前度一次過講清楚而去<br />\n而佢覺得只喺錯少少 <br />\n<br />\n其實我算喺啲咩嘢？<br />\n借我錢同前度開開心心去旅行<br />\n喺咪同前度嚟嗰最後一炮<br />\n究竟喺咩玩法<br />\n喺咪我唔識玩<br />\n喺咪我太易呃<br />\n我仲可以點信任佢<br />\n好攰啦<br />\n<br />\n利申一齊一個月多啲"},{"pid":"96140d3376f8b4cb18758cde87cf0e92e3121d8e","tid":410150,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"個頭綠色"},{"pid":"cf198b7df3ba04266ea73240b1d2192606ac7764","tid":410150,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd9438dea06cf2e91a245932741a98a8f55a1ee","tid":410150,"uid":132361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"愛你何來咁多藉口"},{"pid":"3926fff9d82cc291615aa4da04f015137cd82007","tid":410150,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"Sure"},{"pid":"d664cbc8b460ea59d25487eda55eddd2307ccce2","tid":410150,"uid":139828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}